Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:24.26,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}It's been so long since we left our home behind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:30.51,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Drifting on the Milky Way almost every single day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.98,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where am I supposed to go ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:37.06,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}What're we really looking for ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:42.15,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Stumbling in the darkness, cold and lost
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:49.03,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}But a ray of hope still exists in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:54.54,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Rain or shine, always chase the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:58.67,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Someday, we'll fly across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:02.13,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never fearing anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:06.93,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We'll promise that"we'll go on ! "
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:11.10,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if you're against the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:12.60,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never stop !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:14.35,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Don't look back !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.47,0:22:19.77,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We'll one day rise above it all (never give up)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:23.61,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Who cares if the going's tough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:25.15,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never think !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:27.03,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Keep pushing on !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:34.12,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We can find our promised land
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:24.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}离乡远行 已经历漫长时光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:30.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}年年日日 漂泊在星河八荒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.98,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我欲去往何处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:37.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我在追寻何物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:42.15,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}寒冷 迷茫 在黑暗中流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:49.03,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但我心中仍存一线希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:54.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}无论风雨 始终追寻梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:58.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}总有一天 我们将横越苍茫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:02.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}无所畏惧 展翼翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:06.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我们许下誓言 绝不退让
